{"tid":492872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警官爬高探頭監視同袍如廁捉食煙 廁格警春光乍洩","createTime":"2017-12-08T03:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T07:28:07.000Z","uid":161311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"acfa77b42d4de228c6cd6ca34b76eba6171b8736","tid":492872,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:05:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171208/57554339\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171208%2F57554339&d=WhVtFhm6MzdxFGSq8%2FK8QU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=8d521cbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171208%2F57554339&h=f246b982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171208/57554339</a><br />\n<br />\n長沙灣警署爆出懷疑侵犯私隱風波。有現役警員向《蘋果》投訴，指該署有高層為打擊警署內違規吸煙情況，涉嫌在更衣室爬高探頭監視在廁格內如廁的警員。據悉，有警員上月在廁格內大便時，赫然發現被高層探頭監視，兩人四目交投後，涉事高層以粗口辱罵「X你老味X，你有冇喺入邊食煙！」警方回應指會作跟進。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該高層近日不時親自到更衣室巡察，偷看同袍大便一事更在警署內廣為流傳。駐守長沙灣警署的警員陳先生（化名）稱，曾向受害事主查證，確認事件在署內5樓男更衣室發生，署內不少基層員工脅於高層權威，均敢怒不敢言。<br />\n<br />\n他指，各警署向來也有違規吸煙情況，「你捉食煙係啱，但唔係咁樣捉囉，完全係侵犯私隱。」他又指，受害警員當時根本沒在廁格內吸煙，「唔知佢（涉事高層）係唔係聞到煙味，咁樣伸個頭入去（廁格）裝，畀人發現都唔道歉，仲要用粗口鬧人。」"},{"pid":"73f2817fd2ec64c8f56e5c0991dcfd72b8941a25","tid":492872,"uid":38492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T09:17:40.000Z","msg":"呢到唔準食煙"},{"pid":"892abdf77eadd11c3a0c015c6b700e5739a6fa4c","tid":492872,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢到唔準食煙</blockquote><br />\n唔准裝我痾屎"},{"pid":"03770032fc76793bb2e8f922a8514c9cd5bb19ca","tid":492872,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T09:26:57.000Z","msg":"涉事高層以粗口辱罵「X你老味X，你有冇喺入邊食煙！」警方回應指會作跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩幾巴閉<br />\n偷窺仲要屌返人轉頭"},{"pid":"1a64ffc2db5d312f74cfaf97596022fdd93b6cea","tid":492872,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T09:30:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>涉事高層以粗口辱罵「X你老味X，你有冇喺入邊食煙！」警方回應指會作跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩幾巴閉<br />\n偷窺仲要屌返人轉頭</blockquote><br />\n你班低級警員屢勸不改係要柄喺廁所食煙, 勞煩到大sir親身索著屎除嚟捉人, 唔屌你就有鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caca56e772c37b2a45bcb64b816383750891628d","tid":492872,"uid":39786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T09:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢到唔準食煙</blockquote><br />\n唔准裝我痾屎</blockquote><br />\n你唔食煙我咪唔裝你痾屎囉"},{"pid":"1b7ee689cc7dd9933fe0bd127626ebb60ede8c03","tid":492872,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T09:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢到唔準食煙</blockquote><br />\n唔准裝我痾屎</blockquote><br />\n你唔食煙我咪唔裝你痾屎囉</blockquote><br />\n你唔裝我咪唔食囉"},{"pid":"42476a9b96cb9a01b80dbf55851555cdb690e6d8","tid":492872,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:14:03.000Z","msg":"擺到明死gay佬裝人去廁所 比人發現左就唔想無霸氣兇返人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44448714226b235dce22b49a38674104e6840330","tid":492872,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:28:07.000Z","msg":"GAY"}]}